Subject: [PATCH] arm64/mm: enable ARCH_HAS_VM_GET_PAGE_PROT

References: jsc#PED-1981
Patch-mainline: v5.19-rc1
Git-commit: b3aca728fb276782ab3c851aedaf3d19b33faabe

This defines and exports a platform specific custom vm_get_page_prot() via
subscribing ARCH_HAS_VM_GET_PAGE_PROT. It localizes arch_vm_get_page_prot()
and moves it near vm_get_page_prot().

